summary: Okay, so I love Aggretsuko but the Anai subplot is rubbing me the wrong fucking way. So, let me get this straight. Retsuko is...
body:
Okay, so I love Aggretsuko but the Anai subplot is rubbing me the wrong fucking way.

So, let me get this straight. Retsuko is being more or less reprimanded by everyone around her including her friends, because she….tried to train the new employee at her company? The task she was assigned to do?? And the harshest thing she did was politely correct his behavior answering phones?

People are telling her that she needs to be kind to him and understand how tough it is being a young adult in a new work environment but like…when does the factor that Anai is literally and quite aggressively harassing her come into play here?

She should fucking walk her panda ass to HR and get him fired.
